  "description": "A stunning night view of San Francisco, showcasing a vibrant fireworks display above the city skyline and bridges. The image captures a long exposure shot, illuminating the bridges with a continuous line of light. The foreground features a modern, sleek bridge extending into the dark waters, while in the background, the iconic Golden Gate Bridge is partially visible, adorned with reddish lights. The city skyline is densely packed with illuminated buildings, creating a glittering urban landscape. Fireworks explode in the upper center of the frame, bursting in shades of red, white, and blue, adding a festive and celebratory feel to the scene.",
